msgctxt "37\t178"
msgid ""
"If Arai-san's been taking orders\\n"
"from Katsuragi on the sly..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179\t288"
msgid ""
"Maybe the bullet in Ihara's head\\n"
"was all part of the plan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "302\t473"
msgid ""
"Yeah. A small piece of Katsuragi and\\n"
"Shibata's plot to seize the Tojo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "479\t555"
msgid "Which is where Lily-chan comes in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "563\t668"
msgid "Katsuragi turns on his partner Shibata."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "669\t818"
msgid ""
"And uses her to erase anyone who knew\\n"
"what really happened that day in '85."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "820\t883"
msgid "A real-life femme fatale."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "914\t1048"
msgid ""
"What I'm not piecing together is,\\n"
"why do all that now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1074\t1180"
msgid ""
"He could have snuffed them out\\n"
"decades ago if he wanted."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1191\t1259"
msgid "So why now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1305\t1365"
msgid "He panicked."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1370\t1471"
msgid "Yeah. Something set him off for sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1484\t1545"
msgid "Before he got rid of Ihara..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1546\t1697"
msgid ""
"He had to be certain everyone who knew\\n"
"the truth about '85 was out of the picture."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1731\t1790"
msgid "But why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1791\t1858"
msgid "Maybe he was under orders."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1882\t1980"
msgid "Could be someone else pulling the strings."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1989\t2050"
msgid "Any idea who?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2071\t2209"
msgid "Someone who can't afford to let the truth slip out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2225\t2347"
msgid "Like the top police brass who staged the cover-up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2382\t2434"
msgid "The pieces <Italic>do</Italic> fit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2457\t2566"
msgid "Meaning you've got a rat on the force."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2834\t2949"
msgid "So? You gonna meet up with Mishima?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2950\t3026"
msgid "I think it's worth your time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3041\t3101"
msgid "Agreed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3129\t3173"
msgid "I'm going."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3205\t3258"
msgid "But I'm setting a trap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3261\t3341"
msgid "Oh? What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3346\t3415"
msgid "This Mishima guy..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3415\t3576"
msgid ""
"If he's really the sole survivor of\\n"
"that shooting, he has to know something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3577\t3662"
msgid "Uh-huh. What's your point?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3663\t3792"
msgid ""
"He's a liability.\\n"
"Not just for Katsuragi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3786\t3889"
msgid "But for the traitor on the force, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3902\t3960"
msgid "I get the picture."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3957\t4066"
msgid "You call in your little rendezvous with Mishima..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4067\t4158"
msgid "And hope the traitor comes running."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4310\t4368"
msgid "It's a risky proposal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4383\t4442"
msgid "You sure you're ready?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4494\t4551"
msgid "Positive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4552\t4605"
msgid "Far as I'm concerned..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4631\t4734"
msgid "I'm either gonna solve this thing or die trying."
msgstr ""